---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro";
import Route from "@/components/route/index.astro";
import { ArrowLeftIcon } from "@heroicons/react/24/solid";
---

<style>
  #header {
    background-image: url("/destinations/granada.jpg");
    height: 60vh;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="The Average Cyclist">
  <header
    id="header"
    class="bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-fixed flex items-center justify-center h-screen pb-12"
  >
    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row" id="services">
      <div class="bg-orange px-8">
        <h1
          class="text-6xl mt-2 sm:text-6xl text-center font-mediumrounded-md text-white"
        >
          Granada
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg mt-2 mb-2 font-normal text-center text-white">
          Home of one of the most epic climbs in Europe
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="space-y-20 mt-8">
    <Container>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-12 w-full">
          <p class="mb-4">
            Granada, set against the backdrop of the majestic Sierra Nevada
            mountains in southern Spain, is a captivating destination for
            cyclists. The region offers a unique blend of challenging climbs,
            serene valleys, and picturesque routes that wind through olive
            groves and traditional Andalusian villages. Cycling enthusiasts can
            test their endurance on routes like the iconic climb to Pico Veleta,
            one of the highest paved roads in Europe, or enjoy more leisurely
            rides with stunning views of the Alhambra and the surrounding
            countryside. Granada's rich history, vibrant culture, and varied
            terrain make it a perfect spot for a memorable cycling adventure.
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium leading-none mb-5 mt-8">Routes</h2>

            <div class="flex flex-col w-full mb-5 md:flex-row">
              <Route
                description="Climb one of the highest paved roads in Europe and catch a cold when a world tour pro cyclist flies by."
                title="Sierra Nevada"
                id="destinations/granada/sierranevada"
                distance="80"
                elevation="2000"
              />

              <Route
                title="Ruta de la Cabra"
                description="The Goat's Path is an absolute beauty and must-do when you're in the area."
                id="destinations/granada/lacabra"
                distance="75"
                elevation="1400"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col w-full mb-5 md:flex-row">
              <Route
                title="Around the Sierra de Tejeda"
                description="One of the favorite loops of the pros when preparing for the Tour de France."
                id="destinations/granada/sierradetejeda"
                distance="75"
                elevation="1400"
              />

              <Route
              title="Sierra Nevada: Gran Fondo"
              description="An epic ride with a HC climb to highest paved road in Europe."
              id="destinations/granada/sierranevada-granfondo"
              distance="160"
              elevation="4000"
            />
            </div>

            <a href="/destinations"
              ><span class="inline-flex items-baseline mt-4 mb-2"
                ><ArrowLeftIcon className="size-3 mr-2" /> Back to destinations</span
              ></a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </main></Layout
>
